This paper deals with the problem of goal recognition, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the application of the proposed algorithm in continuous spaces, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO). The algorithm uses heuristics to improve run-time, which is a topic of interest in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of the algorithm in a cooperative robotic team task, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper utilizes a plan recognition by planning (PRP) approach, which is related to programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
